description: Smokin G's is making BBQ with old-school style and sensibilities so that your taste buds get nothing but the best of this low and slow-cooked flavor in every bite! BBQ made the Yankee Way, you'll love the hickory-smoked taste without any unnecessary sauce or spice rubs to distract from the deliciousness these chefs have brought out in the meat. With catering services, couples cooking classes, and so much more, Smokin G's is the perfect truck for every kind of occasion!
name: Smokin G's
